title: Sacha Dunable from Intronaut
itunes:title: Sacha Dunable from Intronaut
description:
I called up my old friend Sacha Dunable from the band Intronaut as well as his custom guitar company, Sacha Dunable Guitars, and dug deep into musicianship, being a "bands band" and the process of making guitars. It was a revealing chat about being in what I call a "working class" band and yet still focusing on being creative. Please donate to the show!
